explore intuitive healing.

00:00:37.230 --> 00:00:42.600 align:middle line:84%
My guest is Dr. Judith Orloff,
author of "Second Sight"

00:00:42.600 --> 00:00:46.710 align:middle line:84%
and also "Dr. Judith Orloff's
Guide to Intuitive Healing."

00:00:46.710 --> 00:00:48.450 align:middle line:90%
