00:08:48.050 --> 00:08:51.170 align:middle line:84%
And that means emotional
healing, physical healing,

00:08:51.170 --> 00:08:52.520 align:middle line:90%
sexual healing.

00:08:52.520 --> 00:08:54.440 align:middle line:84%
And if we really
believe that-- and we

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:56.090 align:middle line:90%
