00:08:56.090 --> 00:08:58.040 align:middle line:84%
It's not just a matter
of thinking it--

00:08:58.040 --> 00:09:01.340 align:middle line:84%
then we must apply it to
everything we ever go through.

00:09:01.340 --> 00:09:03.710 align:middle line:84%
>> But certainly we
