00:09:06.530 --> 00:09:09.290 align:middle line:84%
to a point where it
will stop functioning.

00:09:09.290 --> 00:09:10.090 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:09:10.090 --> 00:09:13.970 align:middle line:84%
>> Then healing, intuitive
