00:09:24.050 --> 00:09:27.680 align:middle line:84%
Because death is a form of
powerful intuitive healing

00:09:27.680 --> 00:09:29.720 align:middle line:90%
that is a wonderful thing.

00:09:29.720 --> 00:09:31.730 align:middle line:84%
