00:09:58.040 --> 00:09:59.450 align:middle line:90%
He became demented.

00:09:59.450 --> 00:10:00.622 align:middle line:90%
Somebody had to walk him.

00:10:00.622 --> 00:10:01.580 align:middle line:90%
He had to wear diapers.

00:10:01.580 --> 00:10:03.110 align:middle line:90%
He lost everything.

00:10:03.110 --> 00:10:06.290 align:middle line:84%
And so as his daughter,
I was his sole caretaker,

00:10:06.290 --> 00:10:08.330 align:middle line:90%
and I was able to be with him.

00:10:08.330 --> 00:10:11.030 align:middle line:84%
And all through his illness
and his dying process,

00:10:11.030 --> 00:10:12.692 align:middle line:90%
I tuned into my intuition.

00:10:12.692 --> 00:10:14.150 align:middle line:84%
When I felt that
the Earth was just

00:10:14.150 --> 00:10:16.010 align:middle line:84%
being ripped apart
beneath my feet,

00:10:16.010 --> 00:10:17.978 align:middle line:90%
I tuned in to my intuition.

00:10:17.978 --> 00:10:20.270 align:middle line:84%
And my intuition said, your
heart has grown this large.

00:10:20.270 --> 00:10:21.320 align:middle line:90%
You can do it.

00:10:21.320 --> 00:10:23.090 align:middle line:84%
As opposed to the
fear, which says,

00:10:23.090 --> 00:10:24.440 align:middle line:90%
oh my god, this is so horrible.

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:25.490 align:middle line:90%
