00:10:25.490 --> 00:10:29.680 align:middle line:84%
Intuition gets us in touch with
our deepest truth and affirms

00:10:29.680 --> 00:10:32.110 align:middle line:84%
who we are, as
opposed to letting

00:10:32.110 --> 00:10:36.100 align:middle line:84%
us become submerged by fears
