00:13:34.850 --> 00:13:36.060 align:middle line:90%
It's not linear.

00:13:36.060 --> 00:13:36.860 align:middle line:90%
It's intuitive.

00:13:36.860 --> 00:13:38.235 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes
you'll have images,

00:13:38.235 --> 00:13:41.280 align:middle line:84%
